<p>
  Dear <b><%= @faculty_sponsor_names %></b>,
</p>
<br />
<p>
Someone has posted a research listing at ResearchMatch, listing you
  as their faculty sponsor.  For this listing to be viewed on the
  website, we'll need your confirmation to prove it's authentic. Here
  is the content of the post that was made:
</p>
<br />
<div class="dashboard_container">
  <div class="dashboard_wrapper_medium">
    <div class="dashboard_container_medium box_shadow">
      <h3><%= @job.title %></h3>
      <p><b>Faculty Sponsor: </b>
          <% @job.faculties.each do |f| %> 
          <%= f.name %> 
          <a href="http://www.google.com/search?btnI=I%27m+Feeling+Lucky&ie=UTF-8&oe=UTF-8&q=<%= f.name %> Berkeley <%= @job.department.name %>" target="_blank">
          <img src="<%= ROOT_URL %>/images/<%= @job.department.name.downcase %>_icon.gif" /> 
          </a>
          <% end %> 
      </p>
      <br />
      <b>Description: </b>
      <p id="description">
      <%= @job.desc %>
      </p>
      
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<br />
<p>
To confirm this listing, please click
<b><a href="<%= activation_url(@job) %>">here</a></b>, or copy and paste the
following URL into your browser:<br />
<b><%= activation_url(@job) %></b>
<br />
</p>
<br />
<p>
  If you believe you have received this e-mail in error, please
  disregard this notice.
</p>
<br />
<p>Regards,</p>
<br />
<p><b>UC Berkeley ResearchMatch<br />
<a href="<%= ROOT_URL %>/"><%= ROOT_URL %>/</a></b>
</p>
